Clojure functions may be invocations from Grails artefacts look like normal
method calls made on a property named @clj@.

{code}
// grails-app/controllers/demo/DemoController.groovy

package demo

class DemoController {

    def add(int x, int y) {
        // this will invoke the add_numbers clojure function...
        def sum = clj.add_numbers(x, y)

        render "The sum of $x and $y is $sum"
    }
}
{code}
